<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-pine mb-8">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-christmas-green/10 p-6 rounded-xl border border-christmas-green/20 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-pine">
          GoodChristmasIdeas.com is reader-supported. When you buy through links on our site, we may
          earn an affiliate commission at no additional cost to you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
        <p>
          To keep this site running and continue providing free gift guides, we participate in
          affiliate marketing programs. This means we earn a small commission when you purchase
          products through our links.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Important:</strong> You never pay more by using our links. The price you pay is the
          same whether you use our affiliate link or go directly to the retailer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Amazon Associates Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          GoodChristmasIdeas.com is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an
          affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees
          by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
        </p>
        <p>
          As an Amazon Associate, we earn from qualifying purchases. Amazon and the Amazon logo are
          trademarks of Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Other Affiliate Partnerships</h2>
        <p>
          In addition to Amazon, we may participate in other affiliate programs including but not
          limited to ShareASale, Commission Junction, Impact, and direct retailer affiliate programs.
          All affiliate relationships are disclosed on this page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Our Editorial Standards</h2>
        <p>
          Our affiliate partnerships do not influence our editorial content. We recommend products
          based on:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Quality and customer reviews</li>
          <li>Value for money</li>
          <li>Relevance to our audience's needs</li>
          <li>Our own research and experience</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We only recommend products we believe will genuinely help our readers find great gifts.
          If a product doesn't meet our standards, we won't recommend it regardless of commission rates.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
        <p>
          In accordance with FTC guidelines, we disclose our affiliate relationships. The Federal Trade
          Commission requires that we are transparent about any financial relationships that may
          influence our content.
        </p>
        <p>
          Links on this website may be affiliate links. Purchases made through these links help support
          our site at no extra cost to you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or how we make recommendations,
          please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We're happy to be transparent about how we operate.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
